<br />

<br />
Example 1. Get into a fight, pet starts attacking on his own, , when one target dies, pet automatically goes to the next available target. I can't believe how helpful this was. I got so tired of sending a pet, only to watch it return to me just as it reached the target because the target died.
<br />

<br />
Example 2. I've only seen it happen once in a 2 hour run thru emain however... Unlessa high RR hunter on my server decided to try to attack my pet last night while outnumbered 8-1, um... he got unstealthed by my granny.<br />_________________<br />Elbarad
